==English==

===Noun Phrase===
'''science fiction'''

# [[Fiction]] in which science and/or technology is a key element.
#: ''Some purists consider the original Star Trek more a Western than science fiction.''
# Technology which, while theoretically possible, is not yet practical.
#: ''Despite decades of research, mass-market personal aircraft are still science fiction.''

